hey%20do%20have%20the%20constitutional%20right%20to%20take%20oath%20as%20Members%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20declared%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20on%20Tuesday.%20While%20radical%20Sikh%20preacher%20Amritpal%20Singh%20won%20Punjab's%20Khadoor%20Sahib%20seat%2C%20terror%20financing%20accused%20Sheikh%20Abdul%20Rashid%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20Engineer%20Rashid%2C%20won%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Baramulla%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEngineer%20Rashid%20has%20been%20lodged%20in%20Tihar%20jail%20since%20August%209%2C%202019%2C%20on%20terror%20funding%20charges.%20Amritpal%20Singh%20was%20arrested%20in%20April%202023%20under%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%20and%20sent%20to%20Assam's%20Dibrugarh%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20now%20arises%20if%20these%20jailed%20newly-elected%20MPs%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20the%20oath%2C%20and%20if%20yes%2C%20how.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20legalities%20involved%2C%20Constitution%20expert%20and%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%20PDT%20Achari%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20following%20the%20constitutional%20provisions%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20sworn%20in%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20is%20a%20constitutional%20right%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20because%20they%20are%20currently%20in%20prison%2C%20Engineer%20Rashid%20and%20Mr%20Singh%20must%20seek%20permission%20from%20authorities%20to%20be%20escorted%20to%20Parliament%20for%20the%20oath%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20they%20have%20taken%20the%20oath%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20return%20to%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20explain%20the%20legalities%2C%20Mr%20Achari%20cited%20Article%20101(4)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20which%20deals%20with%20the%20absence%20of%20members%20from%20both%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20without%20prior%20sanction%20of%20the%20Chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20after%20they%20have%20taken%20the%20oath%2C%20they%20will%20write%20to%20the%20Speaker%2C%20informing%20about%20their%20inability%20to%20attend%20the%20House.%20The%20Speaker%20will%20then%20refer%20their%20requests%20to%20the%20House%20Committee%20on%20Absence%20of%20Members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20will%20recommend%20whether%20the%20member%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20remain%20absent%20from%20House%20proceedings.%20The%20recommendation%20is%20then%20put%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20House%20by%20the%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Engineer%20Rashid%20or%20Mr%20Singh%20are%20to%20be%20convicted%20and%20jailed%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20two%20years%2C%20they%20would%20lose%20their%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20immediately%20as%20per%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgment%20of%202013%2C%20which%20holds%20that%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20would%20be%20disqualified%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20struck%20down%20section%208(4)%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%20which%20earlier%20allowed%20convicted%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20three%20months%20to%20appeal%20against%20their%20convictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717590600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fleodl418_engineer-rashid-amritpal-singh_625x300_05_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-candidates-win-polls-from-prison-what-rules-say-on-jailed-mps-5823426%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20candidates%20currently%20lodged%20in%20prison%20on%20terror%20charges%20emerged%20winners%20in%20the%20just-concluded%20parliamentary%20election%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20an%20unusual%20situation%20for%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20be%20formed%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%