nd%20a%20simultaneous%20Assembly%20election%20to%20return%20as%20Chief%20Minister)%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JDU%20picked%20up%2012%20seats%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-2024-lok-sabha-results-as-bjp-falls-short-of-majority-2-coalition-era-veterans-emerge-kingmakers-5817730%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBJP%20Short%20Of%20Majority%2C%202%20Coalition-Era%20Veterans%20Will%20Be%20Key%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%2028%20MPs%20are%20widely%20seen%20as%20propping%20up%20Mr%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20form%20a%20third%20successive%20union%20government%2C%20or%20risk%20conceding%20ground%20to%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-thanks-allies-chandrababu-naidu-nitish-kumar-in-victory-speech-5817927%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EModi%20Thanks%20Allies%20Naidu%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20In%20Victory%20Speech%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20well-aware%20of%20their%20importance%20to%20the%20NDA%3B%20he%20made%20special%20mention%20to%20the%20TDP%20and%20JDU%20bosses%20during%20his%20victory%20speech%20Tuesday%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20amid%20buzz%20the%20two%20could%20be%20poached%20by%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20(which%20the%20Bihar%20leader%20helped%20found)%2C%20the%20optics%20of%20Mr%20Modi%20flanked%20by%20Mr%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20he%20submits%20his%20bid%20will%20be%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20said%20Mr%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20-%20veteran%20leaders%20well-versed%20in%20the%20art%20of%20coalition%20politics%20-%20could%20be%20courted%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20stake%20claim%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20has%20revealed%20their%20hand%20so%20fa