%20Left%20or%20Congress%20representatives%20from%20her%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Left%20doubted%20her%20integrity%20and%20sincerity%20in%20standing%20together%20as%20a%20bloc%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20President%20of%20the%20West%20Bengal%20unit%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20also%20echoed%20similar%20sentiments%2C%20drawing%20the%20ire%20of%20his%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECut%20to%20the%20results.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Felections%2Fwest-bengal-state-lok-sabha-election-results-2024%5C%22%3EThe%20TMC%20clinched%2029%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20(seven%20more%20than%20its%202019%20performance)%2C%20the%20Left%20none%20(same%20as%20last%20time)%2C%20and%20after%20five%20uninterrupted%20victories%20from%20Baharampur%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-results-live-adhir-ranjan-chowdhury-after-5-terms-as-bharampur-mp-adhir-chowdhury-bowled-out-by-yusuf-pathan-5818468%5C%22%3EChowdhury%20was%20defeated%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20TMC's%20Yusuf%20Pathan.%20The%20Congress%20won%20only%20one%20seat%20against%20two%20in%202019.%20Didi%20was%20back%20in%20the%20reckoning%20after%20a%20short%20period%20of%20uncertainty%20and%20much%20churning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Meeting%20With%20'PK'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20rewind%20a%20bit.%20One%20evening%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%202016%20assembly%20elections%2C%20a%20Trinamool%20MP%20had%20organised%20a%20meeting%20between%20Mamata%20and%20political%20strategist%20Prashant%20Kishor%20(PK)%20at%20the%20party%20headquarters%20in%20Kolkata.%20The%20meeting%20ended%20cordially%20but%20talks%20did%20not%20progress%20further.%20PK%20had%20his%20hands%20full%20at%20the%20time%20and%20the%20TMC%20could%20not%20afford%20his%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20two%20years%20before%20that%20meeting%2C%20the%20TMC%20had%20steamrolled%20the%20opposition%20in%20Parliamentary%20elections%2C%20winning%2034%20of%20the%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Congress%20got%20four%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Left%20managed%20two%20each.%20The%20euphoria%20was%20still%20in%20the%20air%2C%20and%20everybody%20on%20the%20streets%20knew%20who%20was%20winning%20the%20coming%20assembly%20polls.%20The%20TMC%20went%20on%20to%20win%20211%20seats%20in%20the%20294-member%20West%20Bengal%20Legislative%20Assembly%20in%20the%202016%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-bengal-heavyweight-dilip-ghosh-loses-to-trinamools-kirti-azad-5817415%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0BJP's%20Bengal%20Heavyweight%20Dilip%20Ghosh%20Loses%20To%20Trinamool's%20Kirti%20Azad%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20Modi%20wave%20did%20sweep%20the%20state.%20The%20BJP%20increased%20its%20vote%20share%20to%2040%25%20from%2011%25%20in%20the%202016%20elections.%20It%20secured%2018%20seats%20against%20the%20two%20it%20held%20earlier%2C%20while%20the%20TMC%20managed%20to%20win%2022.%20Leaders%20in%20the%20state's%20ruling%20party%20were%20convinced%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20polarising%20the%20state%20and%20getting%20stronger%20by%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Mamata%20Recalibrated%20Her%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnter%20PK.%20After%20a%20two-hour-long%20meeting%20at%20the%20new%20secretariat%20building%2C%20Mamata%20realised%20that%20he%20knew%20more%20about%20the%20state%20and%20its%20poll%20patterns%20than%20she%20had%20anticipated.%20PK%20does%20his%20homework.%20Thus%2C%20the%20public%20health%20expert%20from%20the%20UN%2C%20who%20flew%20in%20from%20Africa%20and%20landed%20in%20India's%20political%20arena%20in%202011%2C%20now%20set%20up%20a%20unit%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20And%20within%20days%20of%20the%20June%202019%20meeting%2C%20changes%20were%20apparent%20-%20from%20launching%20a%20website%2C%20virtual%20access%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20grievance%20cell%2C%20to%20Mamata%20publicly%20slamming%20her%20party%20leaders%20over%20cut-money%2C%20to%20even%20a%20somewhat%20altered%20political%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20time%2C%20she%20got%20involved%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20state%20sometimes%20perhaps%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20missing%20some%20organisational%20matters%20-%20an%20issue%20at%20times%20raised%20in%20different%20quarters.%20Things%20came%20to%20such%20a%20pass%20that%20she%20had%20to%20dissolve%20party%20committees%20and%20reorganise%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fholi-outside-mamata-banerjee-s-residence-in-kolkata-799548%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%C2%A0'Holi'%20Outside%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Residence%20In%20Kolkata%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20elections%20are%20due%20in%20West%20Bengal%20in%202026.%20The%20BJP%20has%20already%20emerged%20as%20the%20principal%20opposition%20party%20in%20the%20state%20with%2077%20seats%20and%20a%2038%25%20vote%20share%20in%20the%20last%20assembly%20polls.%20The%20TMC%20won%20216%20seats%2C%20with%20the%20Left%20and%20Congress%20convincingly%20decimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Siding%20With%20BJP%20Or%20Left-Congress%20Could've%20Been%20Risky%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriven%20by%20such%20regional%20compulsions%2C%20sharing%20a%20common%20platform%20with%20either%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Left-Congress%20combine%20would%20not%20have%20augured%20well%20for%20her%20party.%20She%20had%20formed%20the%20TMC%20in%201998%20after%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20in%20protest%20over%20so-called%20political%20inertia.%20There%20were%20even%20suspicions%20against%20certain%20Congress%20leaders%20for%20being%20in%20cahoots%20with%20the%20then-ruling%20Left%20Front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20has%20always%20acted%20with%20prudence.%20Soon%20after%20forming%20the%20TMC%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20align%20with%20the%20NDA%20to%20strengthen%20herself%20against%20the%20then-ruling%20Left%20Front%20government.%20But%20she%20shifted%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%2C%20eyeing%20over%2030%25%20Muslim%20voters%20who%20were%20then%20supporting%20the%20Left%20Front.%20It%20was%20with%20the%20Congress%20that%20she%20formed%20her%20first%20government%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20another%20lesson%20from%20the%20polls%20in%202024%20and%20those%20preceding%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20Left%20parties'%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20help%20them%20at%20the%20hustings.%20While%20Left%20cadres%20and%20supporters%20voted%20for%20their%20alliance%20partners%2C%20not%20many%20Congress%20votes%20were%20cast%20in%20favour%20of%20Left%20nominees.%20This%20was%20rooted%20in%20over%20three%20decades%20of%20feud%20and%20clashes%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20Red%20bastion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Mamata%20does%20not%20need%20an%20ally%20to%20rule%20West%20Bengal.%20Shrewd%20political%20calculation%2C%20determination%2C%20and%20her%20charisma%20helped%20the%20TMC%20garner%20over%2048%25%20of%20the%20votes%20in%20the%20assembly%20election%20of%202021%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20about%203%25%20over%20her%20victory%20in%202011.%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20share%20gradually%20increased%20from%20about%2040%25%20in%202014%20to%20around%2043%25%20in%202019%2C%20and%20almost%2046%25%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Singular%20Goal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astute%20politician%20she%20is%2C%20Mamata%20anticipated%20a%20third%20term%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20and%20she%20thus%20wanted%20to%20convey%20the%20message%20across%20the%20state%20that%20she%20intended%20to%20stay%20among%20its%20people.%20The%20aim%20is%20another%20resounding%20victory%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20elections.%20Political%20sensibility%20lies%20in%20the%20option%20of%20preparing%20for%20a%20return%20to%20power%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20an%20old%20vs.%20new%20debate%20was%20apparently%20brewing%20within%20her%20party.%20She%20overrode%20reported%20opposition%20from%20a%20section%20of%20the%20TMC%20and%20went%20ahead%20in%20nominating%20septuagenarian%20leaders%20who%20have%20proved%20their%20mettle%20by%20overcoming%20several%20odds%20and%20winning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Jayanta%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%C2%A0writing%20on%20polls%20and%20politics%2C%20conflict%2C%20farmer%20and%20human%20interest%20issues)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717589100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ftc8b0jl8_mamata-banerjee_625x300_22_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffor-mamata-state-power-is-more-important-than-a-shaky-national-stage-5824221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20aim%20is%20another%20resounding%20victory%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20elections.%20Political%20sensibility%20lies%20in%20the%20option%20of%20preparing%20for%20a%20return%20to%20power%20in%20West%20Bengal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffor-mamata-state-power-is-more-important-than-a-shaky-national-stage-5824221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amanda%20Knox%20reconvicted%20in%20slander%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717589037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F78a9%2Flive%2F9fc578b0-231c-11ef-b04e-375672a6fc86.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc877vp7v6lxo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3