%20has%20dealt%20with%20several%20episodes%20of%20panic%20attacks%20and%20mental%20health%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20details%20of%20the%20recent%20incident%2C%20Ms%20Kumari%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20incident%20happened%20on%2022%20April%202024%20when%20I%20was%20subjected%20to%20ethnically%20insensitive%20remarks%20by%20my%20colleague.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shared%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20exacts%20words%20which%20was%20used%20by%20him%20is%20'EK%20CHAMAAT%20MAARENGE%2C%20BIHAR%20PAHUCH%20JAOGI'%20which%20exactly%20means%20-%20I%20will%20slap%20you%20so%20hard%2C%20you%20will%20go%20back%20to%20Bihar.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kumari%20shared%20that%20she%20followed%20the%20protocol%20and%20informed%20her%20manager%20about%20the%20whole%20incident%20but%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20came%20out%20of%20it%26quot%3B.%20A%20team%20meeting%20was%20held%20where%20she%20was%20told%20that%20her%20colleague%20did%20not%20physically%20assault%20her.%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20just%20a%20hatred%20comment%20which%20I%20can%20let%20go%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kumari%20reached%20out%20the%20HR%20team%20and%20filed%20a%20POSH%20Complaint.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20weeks%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20on%203%20May%2C%20I%20received%20an%20email%20from%20the%20HR%20team%20to%20give%20feedback%20for%20the%20same%20without%20any%20updates%20on%20what%20action%20was%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20another%20incident%2C%20Ms%20Kumari%20revealed%20that%20a%20colleague%20made%20objectifying%20remark%20on%20her.%20%26quot%3BThe%20comment%20he%20made%20was%20'Tmhare%20jaisi%20ladki%20hum%20aaj%20tk%20ni%20dekhe%20hai%2C%20akele%20pura%20UK%20team%20ka%20naam%20kharab%20kr%20k%20rkhi%20hai.'%20which%20means%20-%20He%20has%20never%20seen%20a%20girl%20like%20me%2C%20I%20have%20ruined%20the%20name%20of%20their%20team.%20I%20did%20ask%20him%20the%20reason%20for%20saying%20such%20things%20to%20which%20he%20replied%20'tmhare%20alawa%20kisi%20UK%20team%20ki%20ladki%20ko%20hm%20ni%20dkhe%20hai%20cigarette%20pite%20huye'%20which%20means%20-%20he%20has%20never%20seen%20any%20girl%20from%20the%20UK%20team%20smoking%20cigarettes.%20Later%20while%20going%20back%20inside%20the%20office%2C%20I%20saw%20him%20eating%20tobacco%20and%20spitting%20on%20the%20wall%20inside%20the%20office%20premises%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20on%20LinkedIn.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7202948415259828224%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221460%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%2C%20with%20many%20sympathising%20with%20the%20employee%2C%20offering%20words%20of%20reassurance%20and%20encouraging%20him%20to%20find%20a%20better%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BGirl%2C%20you%20have%20got%20guts%20and%20grit.%20Not%20everyone%20has%20it.%20Years%20back%2C%20when%20I%20was%20working%20in%20Tech%20Mahindra%20Noida%2C%20a%20TL%20commented%20on%20one%20of%20our%20colleagues-%20ye%20log%20to%20aise%20Kam%20krtin%20hain%20jaise%20anganwadi%20mein%20kr%20rahi%20hon.%20Reason%3F%20She%20used%20to%20come%20in%20time%20%2C%20and%20leave%20in%20time.%20Unlike%20the%20so%20called%20boss%2C%20she%20hardly%20took%20chai%2C%20sutta%20break%2C%20would%20complete%20assigned%20task....yet%2C%20just%20because%20she%20would%20not%20spend%20extra%20time%20loitering%20around%2C%20TL%20commented.%20Sick!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20user%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BGood%20for%20you%20for%20standing%20up%20for%20yourself.%20Absolutely%20HR%20arrogantly%20swept%20your%20concerns%20of%20the%20toxicity%20you%20faced%20under%20the%20carpet%20for%20no%20one%20to%20see.%20Downplaying%20your%20experience%20allows%20HSBC%20to%20move%20on.%20The%20only%20winners%20is%20HR%20and%20upper%20management.%20The%20toxicity%20will%20grow%20stronger%20every%20time%20these%20bullies%20that%20work%20there%20get%20away%20with%20their%20intimidation%20tactics.%20The%20failure%20of%20HSBC%20to%20act%20on%20such%20vile%20behaviour%20is%20not%20your%20fault.%20Your%20expectations%20of%20a%20truthful%20outcome%20to%20this%20situation%20sadly%20have%20to%20be%20adjusted.%20Your%20behaviour%20however%20should%20not%20be%20disheartening%20in%20any%20way.%20Stay%20strong%2C%20honest%2C%20and%20brave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGood%20work%20Nikita%20%2C%20the%20person%20should%20be%20fired%20from%20the%20company%20to%20set%20an%20example.%20HSBC%20please%20look%20into%20this%20matter.%20It's%20not%20acceptable%2C%20being%20tortured%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20third%20user%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfact%2C%20a%20survey%20conducted%20by%20Harappa%20Insights%20shared%20the%20top%20reasons%20workers%20left%20their%20jobs.%20The%20survey%20revealed%20that%20toxic%20bosses%20and%20toxic%20workplaces%20were%20the%20primary%20%C2%A0reasons%20for%20the%20'Great%20Indian%20Resignation'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717587660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fg4d1q7ho_nitika-kumari_625x300_05_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fone-slap-you-will-reach-woman-shares-toxic-workplace-experience-sparks-conversation-5824181%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ms%20Kumari%20mentioned%20that%20she%20has%20dealt%20with%20several%20episodes%20of%20panic%20attacks%20and%20mental%20health%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fone-slap-you-will-reach-woman-shares-toxic-workplace-experience-sparks-conversation-5824181%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fone-slap-you-will-re