s%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-to-stay-in-jail-request-for-interim-bail-dismissed-5823575%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-to-stay-in-jail-request-for-interim-bail-dismissed-5823575%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Mayawati%20Said%20About%20Muslims%20As%20BSP%20Scores%20Zero%20In%202024%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20scoring%20a%20zero%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20president%20Mayawati%20today%20said%20that%20despite%20the%20party%20gave%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bproper%20representation%26quot%3B%20in%20elections%2C%20the%20Muslim%20community%20is%20not%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20BSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20the%20party%20will%20give%20the%20community%20an%20electoral%20opportunity%20only%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP%20had%20failed%20to%20open%20its%20account%20in%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20as%20well.%20It%2C%20however%2C%20bagged%2010%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20one%2C%20which%20it%20had%20fought%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayawati%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20that%20her%20party%20will%20do%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20analysis%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20trouncing%20and%20will%20take%20whatever%20steps%20that%20are%20necessary%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20expressed%20her%20gratitude%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community%2C%20especially%20the%20Jatavs%2C%20for%20supporting%20the%20party%2C%20but%20also%20expressed%20her%20displeasure%20towards%20the%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Muslim%20community%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%2C%20is%20not%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20BSP%20properly%20despite%20being%20given%20proper%20representation%20in%20the%20past%20elections%20and%20this%20time%20also%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha