2canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fmumbai-welcomes-seasons-first-pre-monsoon-showers%2Farticleshow%2F110733071.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Price%20Must%20BJP%20Pay%20To%20Keep%20Kingmakers%20JDU%2C%20TDP%20On%20Board%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20defied%20exit%20polls%20and%20denied%20a%20clear%20majority%20to%20the%20incumbent%20BJP%2C%20its%20allies%2C%20and%20now%20kingmakers%2C%20JDU's%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20TDP's%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20have%20reached%20Delhi%20for%20an%20NDA%20meeting%20this%20evening%20that%20will%20decide%20on%20the%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20buzz%20that%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20which%20has%20sprung%20a%20surprise%20by%20winning%20232%20seats%2C%20will%20try%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Mr%20Kumar%20and%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20both%20JDU%20and%20TDP%20have%20stressed%20that%20they%20will%20stay%20with%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20won%20240%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20--%2032%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark.%20TDP%20and%20JDU%20together%20hold%2028%20seats%20and%20along%20with%20BJP's%20other%20allies%2C%20NDA%20will%20be%20past%20the%20magic%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Mr%20Naidu%20and%20Mr%20Kumar%20--%20both%20Coalition-era%20veterans%20--%20are%20skilled%20in%20the%20art%20of%20bargaining%20and%20know%20how%20to%20make%20their%20support%20count.%20If%20the%20BJP%20crossed%20the%20majority%20mark%20on%20its%20own%2C%20allies%20would%20have%20to%20be%20happy%20with%20what%20they%20got%2C%20but%20the%20numbers%20have%20opened%20a%20window%20of%20opportunity%20and%20the%20veterans%20won't%20miss%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20JDU%20has%20hinted%20what%20it%20may%20ask%20for%2C%20TDP%20has%20been%20tight-lipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20senior%20JDU%20leader%20KC%20Tyagi%20said%20the%20party%20will%20consider%20joining%20the%20government%20%26quot%3Bif%20an%20invitation%20is%20extended%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20the%20new%20government%20to%20consider%20giving%20special%20category%20status%20to%20Bihar%20and%20conduct%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tyagi%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20these%20are%20not%20conditions%20for%20JDU's%20support%20to%20NDA.%20%26quot%3BOur%20support%20is%20unconditional.%20But%20the%20unemployment%20in%20Bihar%20will%20not%20end%20till%20Bihar%20gets%20special%20status.%20So%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20support%20NDA%20has%20received%20from%20Bihar%2C%20we%20hope%20there%20will%20be%20an%20initiative%20to%20give%20Bihar%20special%20status%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20caste%20census%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20key%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20this%20election.%20Ahead%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20latest%20flip-flop%2C%20his%20coalition%20government%20with%20RJD%20and%20Congress%20had%20also%20conducted%20a%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar.%C2%A0%26quot%3BNarendra%20Modi%20has%20never%20opposed%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20census.%20Time%20demands%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tyagi%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20there%20is%20little%20clarity%20on%20what%20he%20may%20demand%20from%20the%20BJP%20leadership.%20TDP%20sources%20suggest%20that%20the%20party%20may%20ask%20for%20plum%20ministries%20at%20the%20Centre.%20A%20preferential%20status%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20is%20another%20key%20issue%20that%20may%20come%20up%20in%20the%20negotiations.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20a%20dispute%20over%20a%20special%20status%20demand%20that%20had%20prompted%20Mr%20Naidu%20to%20part%20ways%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20TDP%20chief%2C%20who%20has%20returned%20to%20power%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20with%20a%20thumping%20win%2C%20the%20task%20is%20cut%20out.%20The%20massive%20mandate%20for%20his%20party%20has%20come%20on%20a%20promise%20to%20rebuild%20the%20state%20and%20to%20develop%20a%20capital%20city.%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20first%20CEO%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20his%20record%20of%20promoting%20ease%20of%20business%20and%20developing%20cities%2C%20has%20to%20ensure%20he%20delivers%20on%20his%20promises.%20More%20so%20to%20secure%20his%20son%20Nara%20Lokesh's%20political%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20both%20the%20TDP%20and%20JDU%20stress%20that%20they%20are%20firmly%20with%20NDA%2C%20but%20when%20the%20two%20kingmakers%20are%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20no%20possibility%20can%20be%20ruled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717582200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fb40b1rr_nitish-naidu-split_625x300_04_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-chandrababu-naidu-nitish-kumar-what-price-must-bjp-pay-to-keep-kingmakers-jdu-tdp-on-board-5823452%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20after%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20defied%20exit%20polls%20and%20denied%20a%20clear%20majority%20to%20the%20incumbent%20BJP%2C%20its%20allies%2C%20and%20now%20kingmakers%2C%20JDU's%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20TDP's%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20have%20reached%20Delhi%20for%20an%20NDA%20meeting%20this%20evening%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-chandrababu-naidu-nitish-kumar-what-price-must-bjp-pay-to-keep-kingmakers-jdu-tdp-on-board-5823452%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-chandrababu-naidu-nitish-kumar-what-price-must-bjp-pay-to-keep-kingmakers-jdu-tdp-on-board-5823452%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fi