0over%205%20million%20outlets%20across%20the%20country%2C%20Coca-Cola%20is%20expanding%20the%20presence%20of%20its%20coolers%20to%20every%20corner%20of%20India.%20With%20India%20achieving%20100%20percent%20electrification%20of%20villages%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekiranas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20fast-growing%20network%20of%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20large%20retailers%20now%20effortlessly%20use%20the%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20as%20part%20of%20their%20shop%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20bringing%20to%20reality%20what%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20former%20president%20Robert%20Woodruff%20famously%20said%20about%20winning%20in%20the%20beverage%20market%20%E2%80%94%20delivering%20its%20products%20%E2%80%9Cwithin%20an%20arm%E2%80%99s%20reach%20of%20desire%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20any%20desire%3A%20The%20desire%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F293356%2Fhealth-benefits-of-kanji-fermented-rice-water-ancient-south-india-food-science%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecool%2C%20refreshing%20beverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20any%20occasion%20%E2%80%94%20after%20a%20delightful%20lunch%2C%20an%20exciting%20evening%20of%20cricket%2C%20or%20a%20quick%20gulp%20after%20a%20shopping%20stroll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBoosting%20retailer%20revenue%20and%20consumer%20experience%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola%E2%80%99s%20coolers%20are%20now%20contributing%20to%20increased%20revenues%20for%20retailers%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20micro%2C%20small%2C%20and%20medium%20players%2C%20many%20of%20them%20having%20access%20to%20coolers%20following%20the%20electrification%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20consumers%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20evident%3A%20Not%20only%20do%20they%20have%20a%20chilled%20beverage%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20assured%20of%20its%20purity%20and%20hygiene.%20They%20also%20present%20them%20with%20an%20array%20of%20options%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20diversity%20that%20a%20Coca-Cola%20cooler%2C%20with%20exclusive%20rack%20space%20for%20its%20products%2C%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20retailers%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20manifold.%20One%2C%20the%20advent%20of%20more%20coolers%2C%20especially%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20has%20helped%20attract%20new%20consumers%2C%20increasing%20their%20share%20of%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297294%2Fhistory-origin-of-south-india-iconic-drinks-filter-coffee-jigarthanda-tamil-nadu-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enon-alcoholic%20beverages%3C%2Fa%3E%20market%20is%20growing%20at%20a%20CAGR%20of%208.7%20percent%20to%20INR%201%2C47%2C233%20crores%20by%202030%2C%20and%20by%20product%20categories%2C%20Indians%20consume%20carbonated%20beverages%20the%20most%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20for%20Research%20on%20International%20Economic%20Relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20introduction%20of%20coolers%20has%20given%20many%20retailers%20a%20boost%20%E2%80%94%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20those%20who%20continue%20to%20sell%20them%20either%20stored%20in%20the%20open%20or%20tucked%20into%20ice%20bags.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20the%20optics%20of%20flaunting%20a%20cooler%2C%20it%20is%20the%20purity%20and%20hygiene%20associated%20with%20a%20refrigerated%20cooler%20that%20influences%20consumer%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20retailers%20through%20the%20Superpower%20Retailer%20Program%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Prasad%2C%20a%20retailer%20on%20Park%20Street%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20says%20that%20introducing%20the%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20has%20helped%20reshape%20his%20business%2C%20enabling%20him%20to%20stock%20up%20more%20products%2C%20all%20resulting%20in%20more%20sales.%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20Abhishek%20Pathak%20says%20beverage%20sales%20have%20soared%20since%20the%20installation%20of%20Coca-Cola%20India%20coolers%2C%20which%20keep%20the%20beverages%20refreshingly%20chilled%20and%20help%20attract%20more%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Retail%20business%20owners%20with%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20in%20their%20kirana%20stores%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352124%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20Pathak%20(L)%20and%20Anil%20Prasad%20(R)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20India%2C%20approximately%2020%20percent%20of%20a%20retailer%E2%80%99s%20income%20is%20generated%20from%20beverage%20sales%2C%20with%206%C2%A0%20percent%20specifically%20attributed%20to%20the%20sale%20of%20Coca-Cola%20beverages.%20The%20introduction%20of%20coolers%20has%20ramped%20up%20sales%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola%20India%E2%80%99s%20Superpower%20Retailer%20Program%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20transformation%20%E2%80%94%20a%20three-year%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Corporation%20(NSDC)%20under%20the%20Skill%20India%20Mission%2C%20focusing%20on%20empowering%20small%20retailers%20in%20the%20states%20of%20Odisha%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20expand%20to%20more%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20empowers%20retailers%20by%20building%20their%20capacity%20and%20capability%20in%20modern%20retailing%20and%20provides%20training%20to%20small%20and%20micro%20retailers%2C%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20knowledge%20and%20skills%20needed%20to%20better%20understand%20consumer%20behaviours%20and%20preferences.%20Amanpreet%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20%E2%80%989%20to%209%E2%80%99%20store%2C%20says%20the%20programme%20has%20helped%20in%20providing%20customers%20with%20refreshing%20beverages%20using%20coolers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInnovation%20in%20cooler%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20100%20percent%20rural%20electrification%20was%20being%20implemented%2C%20when%20many%20villages%20remained%20unconnected%20in%20the%202010s%2C%20Coca-Cola%20distributed%20eKOCool%20solar%20coolers%20free%20of%20cost%20to%20its%20vendors.%20A%20product%20innovation%20that%20was%20not%20only%20used%20for%20chilling%20beverages%20but%20also%20for%20charging%20mobile%20phones.%20This%20model%20was%20replicated%20across%20several%20countries%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possibilities%20of%20digital%20technologies%20have%20now%20become%20further%20evident.%20With%20the%20remarkable%20advances%20in%20cooler%20technology%2C%20Coca-Cola%20coolers%20stand%20out%20for%20their%20digital%20signage%20and%20enhanced%20design%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20an%20ongoing%20focus%20on%20replacing%20older%20ones%20with%20hydrofluorocarbon-free%20and%20more%20energy-efficient%20coolers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobally%20for%20Coca-Cola%2C%20in%202022%2C%2088%20percent%20of%20all%20new%20coolers%20placed%20were%20HFC-free.%20This%20is%20an%20increase%20from%2061%20percent%20of%20coolers%20placed%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20further%20builds%20on%20Coca-Cola%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F305877%2Fpernod-ricard-india-launches-one-for-our-planet-initiative-reduce-monocarton-packaging%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommitment%20to%20the%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20society%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98Our%20Planet%20Matters%E2%80%99%20strategy.%20The%20bottom%20line%20of%20this%20is%20to%20bring%20transformational%20and%20radical%20change%20through%20a%20comprehensive%20approach%20to%20social%2C%20environmental%2C%20and%20economic%20stewardship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20are%20being%20realised%20on%20the%20ground%20with%20the%20humble%20cooler%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20bringing%20more%20revenue%20to%20grassroots-level%20retailers%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20happiness%20quotient%20of%20customers%2C%20and%20enabling%20economies%20with%20a%20more%20vibrant%20retail%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717573465000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FUntitled-design-5-1717573892.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352095%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Coca-Cola%20coolers%20are%20becoming%20ubiquitous%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20urban%20and%20rural%20retail%20outlets%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20village%20electrification%20and%20boosting%20revenues%20for%20small%20to%20medium%20retailers.%20Know%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TBI%20Team%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F352095%2Fcoca-cola-beverage-cooler-superpower-retailer-program-small-medium-business%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCar%20Is%20Sent%203%20Hours%20Away%20For%20A%20Burger%26quot%3B%3A%20Anurag%20Kashyap%20On%20Stars'%20Demands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fimtiaz-ali-to-anurag-kashyap-can-you-name-all-the-directors-in-zoya-akhtars-throwback-pic-5785254%5C%22%3EDirector%20Anurag%20Kashyap%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20budget%20and%20the%20revenue%20of%20films.%20Talking%20about%20how%20a%20film's%20budget%20is%20spent%20on%20%E2%80%9Cparaphernalia%E2%80%9D%2C%20Anurag%20Kashyap%20told%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-a8C3kZbxyo%5C%22%3EHumans%20of%20Cinema%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20spending%20the%20money%20on%20the%20film.%20People%20need%20to%20come%20back%20to%20this%20whole%20reality%20check.%20One%20thing%20people%20need%20to%20understand%20is%20that%20when%20we%20make%20a%20film%2C%20we're%20working%2C%20we're%20creating%20something.%20It's%20not%20a%20holiday%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20picnic.%20A%20lot%20of%20money%20that%20is%20spent%20doesn't%20go%20into%20making%20the%20film.%20It%20goes%20into%20the%20paraphernalia%3B%20it%20goes%20into%20the%20entourage.%20You're%20shooting%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20jungle%2C%20but%20one%20car%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20city%20three%20hours%20away%20specifically%20to%20get%20you%20that%20five-star%20burger%20you%20want.%20You%20don't%20get%20into%20the%20process%20of%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmaharaja-trailer-vijay-sethupathi-and-anurag-kashyap-in-a-revenge-saga-5783835%5C%22%3EAnurag%20Kashyap%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20said%20that%20independent%20ideas%20are%20not%20getting%20the%20backing.%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20mainstream%2C%20independent%20ideas%20work%20much%20more.%20But%20the%20thing%20is%20they%20don't%20get%20the%20backing.%20Today%20you%20go%20to%20any%20actor%2C%20any%20star.%20They%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20whether%20it%20(the%20project)%20is%20a%20big%20project%20or%20not%2C%20whether%20it%20will%20be%20hit%20or%20not%2C%20whether%20it%20will%20make%20business%20or%20not.%20They%20think%20that%20%E2%80%98the%20script%20is%20good%20but%20what%20can%20we%20do%20so%20that%20it%20earns%20more'.%20If%20the%20script%20is%20good%2C%20they%20must%20do%20it.%20Everybody%20starts%20thinking%20of%20what%20will%20happen%20after%20the%20film%20comes%20out.%20But%20nobody%20is%20going%20by%20instinct.%20We%20all%20are%20very%20caught%20up%20in%20this.%20And%20social%20media%20is%20the%20biggest%20culprit%20in%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmanoj-bajpayee-breaks-silence-on-rift-with-filmmaker-anurag-kashyap-5727731%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGangs%20of%20Wasseypur%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0director%3C%2Fa%3E%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20film's%20business%20has%20taken%20over%20everyone.%20Everybody%20is%20talking%20about%20the%20box%20office%20numbers.%20And%20in%20a%20time%20like%20today%20when%20people%20are%20actually%20making%20much%20more%20money%20than%20they%20would%20have%2020%20years%20ago%20they%20feel%20short-changed.%20When%20I%20was%20working%20as%20a%20writer%2C%20my%20fees%20for%20the%20entire%20film%20were%20less%20than%20what%20a%20first%20AD%20would%20get%20per%20month%20today.%20But%20I%20cannot%20make%20a%20film%20today%20like%20I%20made%C2%A0%3Cem%3EGulaal%2C%20Raman%20Raghav%202.0%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EUgly%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20because%20of%20politics%20as%20well%20as%20budgeting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnurag%20Kashyap%20also%20shared%20an%20instance%20from%20his%202018%20series%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESacred%20Games.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20budget%20the%20film%20at%20that%20cost%2C%20today%2C%20because%20when%20OTTs%20came%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20got%20spoiled.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20had%20never%20seen%20so%20many%20vanity%20vans%20on%20my%20set%20as%20I%20had%20seen%20on%20Sacred%20Games.%20That's%20how%20the%20culture%20got%20started.%20Then%20you%20can't%20reverse%20that.%20Finally%2C%20those%20people%20started%20getting%20paid%20who%20were%20totally%20ignored%2C%20which%20is%20the%20technical%20crew%2C%20who%20work%20the%20longest%20on%20a%20film.%20They%20come%20in%20first%2C%20they%20leave%20last.%20The%20actor%20comes%2C%20shoots%20and%20goes.%20But%20people%20who%20were%20least%20paid%20started%20getting%20paid%2C%20in%20a%20kind%20of%20fair%20way.%20But%20a%20lot%20of%20extra%20things%20started%20coming%20in.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%20you%20cannot%20go%20from%20there.%20The%20reversing%20will%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20gaps%20now.%20It%20will%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%20Actors%20have%20to%20revise%20their%20prices.%20Now%2C%20OTTs%20have%20also%20realised%20this.%20Everyone%20wants%20to%20cut%20down%20costs%20now.%20What%20has%20happened%20is%2C%20initially%20everyone%20raised%20the%20cost%2C%20but%20now%20they%20want%20to%20cut%20it%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717573320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fsj477mog_anurag_625x300_05_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fanurag-kashyap-opens-up-on-budget-and-revenue-of-films-in-today-s-world-5822259%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20money%20that%20is%20spent%20doesn't%20go%20into%20making%20the%20film.%20It%20goes%20into%20the%20paraphernalia%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anurag%20Kashyap%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fanurag-kashyap-opens-up-on-budget-and-revenue-of-films-in-today-s-world-5822259%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fanurag-kashyap-opens-up-on-budget-and-revenue-of-films-in-today-s-world-5822259%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fanurag-kashyap-opens-up-on-budget-and-revenue-of-films-in-today-s-world-5822259%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20X%20Updates%20Content%20Policies%2C%20Officially%20Allows%20Porn.%20Details%20Here%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-says-will-ensure-porn-free-mode-on-x-platform-5821434%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20platform%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20has%20officially%20announced%20a%20shift%20in%20its%20content%20policies%2C%20now%20permitting%20pornographic%20material.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSafety%2Fstatus%2F1797669613775282677%C2%A0%C2%A0%5C%22%3Ea%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20X%20announced%20the%20launch%20of%20updated%20policies%20regarding%20%E2%80%9CAdult%20Content%20and%20Violent%20Content%E2%80%9D%20on%20its%20platform.%20These%20new%20policies%20aim%20to%20provide%20greater%20%E2%80%9Cclarity%E2%80%9D%20regarding%20the%20rules%20governing%20such%20content%20and%20increase%20%E2%80%9Ctransparency%20in%20their%20enforcement%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThese%20policies%20replace%20the%20%E2%80%9Cformer%20Sensitive%20Media%20and%20Violent%20Speech%20policies%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20said%2C%20even%20though%20the%20underlying%20principles%20of%20enforcement%20remain%20unchanged.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnX's%20policy%20also%20extends%20to%20AI-generated%20and%20animated%20content.%20The%20platform%20permits%20adult%20nudity%20or%20sexual%20content%2C%20including%20AI-generated%2C%20photographic%2C%20or%20animated%20projections.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EWhat%20X%20means%20by%20%E2%80%98Adult'%20and%20%E2%80%98Violent'%20content%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThey%20clarified%20that%20%E2%80%9CAdult%20Content%20covers%20our%20approach%20to%20sharing%20consensual%20sexual%20content%20and%20adult%20nudity%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CViolent%20Content%20covers%20violent%20speech%20and%20violent%20media%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20more%20holistic%20approach%20to%20combating%20violence%20in%20all%20forms.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BAdult%20content%26quot%3B%20will%20show%20full%20or%20partial%20nudity%2C%20including%20close-ups%20of%20genitals%2C%20buttocks%20or%20breasts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20explicit%20or%20implied%20sexual%20behaviour%20or%20simulated%20acts%20like%20sexual%20intercourse.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EHow%20to%20mark%20content%20on%20X%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20users%20who%20frequently%20share%20adult%20content%20on%20X%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelp.x.com%2Fen%2Frules-and-policies%2Fadult-content%C2%A0%5C%22%3Eplatform%20suggests%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadjusting%20their%20media%20settings%20accordingly.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20will%20ensure%20such%20images%20and%20videos%20are%20placed%20behind%20a%20content%20warning%2C%20which%20pops%20up%20before%20they%20are%20viewed.%20There%20is%20also%20the%20option%20to%20add%20a%20one-time%20content%20warning%20to%20individual%20posts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnX%20also%20said%20that%20if%20anyone%20doesn't%20mark%20their%20posts%20correctly%2C%20the%20platform%20will%20do%20it%20for%20them.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EHarmful%20content%20will%20be%20prohibited%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20platform%20will%20continue%20to%20ban%20pornographic%20content%20that%20is%20harmful%20or%20non-consensual%2C%20as%20well%20as%20any%20material%20that%20promotes%20the%20objectification%20of%20people%20or%20harm%20to%20minors.%20Moreover%2C%20adult%20content%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20in%20profile%20pictures%2C%20banners%20or%20other%20publicly%20visible%20areas.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EHow%20to%20report%20content%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20report%20unmarked%20content%20or%20any%20other%20violations%2C%20use%20the%20%E2%80%98report'%20option%20on%20the%20app.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EPolicy%20for%20underage%20users%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20the%20policy%2C%20users%20under%2018%20or%20those%20who%20haven't%20provided%20their%20birth%20date%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20view%20posts%20marked%20as%20adult%20content.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20decision%2C%20announced%20on%20Monday%2C%20marks%20a%20significant%20change%20in%20what%20is%20permissible%20on%20the%20platform%20and%20arrives%20amid%20pressure%20to%20protect%20children%20from%20looking%20at%20inappropriate%20content%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717569600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ftl29m2d_x-generic_625x300_09_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-updates-policies-officially-allows-porn-details-here-5822048%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20has%20officially%20announced%20a%20shift%20in%20its%20content%20policies%2C%20now%20permitting%20pornographic%20material.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-updates-policies-officially-allows-porn-details-here-5822048%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-updates-policies-officially-allows-porn-details-here-5822048%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-updates-policies-officially-allows-porn-details-here-5822048%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paris%20Hilton%20among%20users%20targeted%20in%20TikTok%20hack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717569169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F39e2%2Flive%2Ffa691610-22e9-11ef-82fe-93235f4d3d4b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcl770d121gro%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20video-sharing%20app%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20limited%26quot%3B%20number%20of%20accounts%20had%20been%20compromised.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3