0senders%20of%20these%20emails%20include%20from%20multinational%20companies%20like%20Oracle%2C%20Apple%2C%20Intel%2C%20Mcdonald%E2%80%99s%20and%20the%20latest%20one%20from%20NASA%20(The%20National%20Aeronautics%20and%20Space%20Administration).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20self-taught%2022-year-old%20from%20Zungalpora%2C%20Kulgam%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20has%20carved%20a%20path%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20ethical%20hacking%20and%20cyber%20security%20space.%20He%20worked%20hard%20towards%20his%20goal%20while%20grappling%20with%20limited%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20and%20spotty%20electricity.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20feather%20on%20his%20cap%20has%20been%20his%20work%20for%20Apple%20and%20NASA.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20discovered%20a%20critical%20vulnerability%20in%20Apple%20which%20could%20have%20compromised%20the%20data%20of%20thousands%20of%20its%20users.%20Apple%20acknowledged%20his%20discovery%20and%20featured%20him%20in%20its%20Hall%20of%20Fame%20in%20August%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20US%20space%20agency%2C%20he%20discovered%20unknown%20vulnerabilities%20through%20their%20vulnerability%20disclosure%20programme%20which%20earned%20him%20a%20name%20in%20their%20Hall%20of%20Fame%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20spent%20hours%20helping%20these%20companies%20secure%20their%20data%2C%20earning%20him%20millions%20of%20dollars%20besides%20validation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20his%20story%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20go-to%20techie%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuneeb%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20computers%20began%20at%20the%20age%20of%20nine.%20He%20would%20hack%20into%20his%20friend%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20accounts%20and%20the%20Wif-Fi%20servers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6rJQ9XPgHJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20r