ical%20gardening%20using%20PVC%20pipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20has%20installed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284723%2Fvertical-garden-pvc-pipes-bamboo-organic-vegetables-how-to-terrace-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPVC%20pipes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20create%20a%20vertical%20garden%20where%20she%20grows%20around%205%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mithilesh%20says%20that%20using%20PVC%20pipes%20saves%20space%20as%20well%20as%20money.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20general%2C%20PVC%20pipes%20are%20cheap%2C%20easy%20to%20find%2C%20and%20can%20save%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20does%20not%20require%20a%20complicated%20set%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunita%20harvests%20at%20least%205%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20week.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunita%20harvests%20at%20least%205%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20week.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ingenious%20gardeners%20share%20gardening%20tips%20for%20creating%20a%20vertical%20garden%20using%20PVC%20pipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.Take%20a%20five-foot%20pipe%20and%20cut%20it%20into%20sections%20according%20to%20the%20number%20of%20saplings%20or%20seeds%20you%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Avoid%20drilling%20an%20excessive%20number%20of%20holes%20in%20the%20pipe.%20Maintain%20a%20distance%20of%2018%20inches%20between%20holes%20on%20one%20side%20and%20a%20gap%20of%20nine%20inches%20on%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20pipe.%20In%20total%2C%20there%20should%20be%20five%20evenly%20spaced%20holes%20along%20a%20six-foot%20pipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Close%20the%20extra%20holes%2C%20if%20any%2C%20using%20a%20hot%20air%20gun.%20Do%20not%20forget%20to%20tape%20the%20extra%20holes%20to%20prevent%20water%20leakage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Fill%20three-fourth%20part%20of%20the%20pipe%20with%20soil%20and%20plant%20the%20seed%20or%20sapling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Add%20a%20mixture%20of%20vermicompost%20or%20any%20other%20organic%20fertiliser%20to%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Create%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20soil%20and%20fill%20it%20with%20sand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20Water%20the%20sand%20so%20that%20it%20stays%20wet%20and%20the%20moisture%20reaches%20the%20bottom%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20change%20the%20soil%20for%20the%20next%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20New%20saplings%20or%20seeds%20can%20be%20planted%20by%20simply%20making%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Neem%20water%20can%20be%20used%20to%20avoid%20pests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGardening%20in%20two%20five-foot%20PVC%20pipes%20typically%20costs%20around%20Rs%201%2C000.%20With%20this%20setup%2C%20you%20can%20cultivate%20four%20to%20five%20varieties%20of%20vegetables%2C%20ranging%20from%20leafy%20greens%20to%20tubers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20