%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reach%20women%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20Asan%20also%20has%20a%20comprehensive%20behavioural%20change%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20programme%20to%20onboard%20and%20educate%20people%20on%20using%20the%20Asan%20Cup.%20The%20key%20to%20our%20behavioural%20change%20model%20is%20that%20education%20must%20come%20from%20a%20trusted%20source.%20For%20example%2C%20as%20someone%20from%20Bengaluru%20whose%20first%20language%20is%20English%2C%20I%20might%20not%20be%20a%20trusted%20source%20in%20a%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20we%20hired%20local%20social%20workers%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20use%20the%20cups%20themselves.%20They%20then%20trained%20rural%20women%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20cup%2C%20which%20eliminated%20scepticism%20because%20the%20information%20was%20coming%20from%20a%20trusted%20source.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20Asan%20Cup%20the%20company%20sells%2C%20they%20donate%20one%20for%20free%2C%20primarily%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317722%2Fmumbai-entrepreneurs-start-marketplace-for-ngo-products-jhappi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20through%20their%20NGO%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20rural%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20collaborate%20with%20various%20NGO%20partners%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20factories%20to%20offer%20subsidised%20schemes%2C%20making%20the%20Asan%20Cup%20more%20accessible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIra%20engages%20with%20women%20from%20SHG%2C%20trains%20them%20and%20then%20sends%20them%20to%20villages%20to%20introduce%20women%20with%20the%20Asan%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ira%20Guha%2C%20founder%20of%20Asan%20Cup.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351636%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIra%20Guha%2C%20founder%20of%20Asan%20Cup.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20recipient%20receives%20a%20clutch%20storage%20pouch%2C%20a%20user%20manual%20in%20their%20local%20language%2C%20and%20a%20detailed%20educational%20session%20conducted%20by%20a%20local%20health%20worker.%20They%20also%20receive%20the%20health%20worker%E2%80%99s%20contact%20for%20follow-up%20sessions%20over%20the%20next%20six%20months.%20This%20comprehensive%20programme%20ensures%20that%20everyone%20has%20the%20resources%20and%20support%20needed%20to%20safely%20use%20the%20Asan%20Cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20she%20has%20reached%20out%20to%2015%2C000%20women%20in%2060%20villages%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Kanakapura.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20single%20woman%20in%20those%20areas%20are%20using%20the%20Asan%20cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagamma%2C%2036%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Kanakapura%2C%20complained%20that%20she%20can%E2%80%99t%20wear%20her%20favourite%20white%20sarees%20fearing%20stains%20during%20her%20periods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20have%20been%20using%20the%20Asan%20cup%20for%20several%20months%20now%20and%20the%20scenario%20has%20changed.%20The%20line%20between%20the%20period%20and%20non-period%20days%20has%20blurred.%20I%20have%20recommended%20it%20to%20my%20niece%20now%20as%20well.%20The%20pads%20used%20to%20give%20me%20rashes%20on%20the%20thighs%20but%20now%20there%20are%20no%20such%20issues.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20I%20wear%20whatever%20colour%20saree%20I%20want%20without%20any%20fear%20of%20stains%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayalakshmi%2C%2038%2C%20highlighted%20that%20she%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321703%2Fiit-material-scientists-innovate-biodegradable-super-absorbent-sheets-for-sanitary-pads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20the%20used%20pads%20in%20a%20plastic%20bag%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20burn%20them.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20other%20choice%2C%20I%20just%20burned%20them%20when%20no%20one%20was%20watching.%20But%20not%20with%20the%20Asan%20cup%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20that.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20used%20to%20hate%20travelling%20to%20work%20while%20wearing%20a%20pad%20in%20the%20heat%20but%20now%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20any%20discomfort%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Asan%20continuously%20reaches%20women%20in%20rural%20India%2C%20Ira%20believes%20that%20her%20work%20is%20not%20over.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20still%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20women%20using%20rags%20and%20lacking%20any%20access%20to%20menstrual%20hygiene.%20If%20even%20one%20woman%20is%20without%20access%20to%20menstrual%20hygiene%2C%20my%20job%20is%20not%20over.%20As%20a%20company%2C%20we%20want%20to%20eradicate%20period%20poverty%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20pictures%20credit%3A%20Ira%20Guha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717079206000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20cups%20come%20with%20a%20cloth%20bag%20and%20a%20instruction%20manual%20in%20the%20local%20language.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351606%2Fmenstrual-cups-made-in-india-asan-cup-how-to-use-ira-guha-period-hygiene-for-rural-women-karnataka%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Organic%20Tea%20Tasting%20%26amp%3B%20Waterfall%20Picnics%3A%20Eco-Stay%20in%20Coonoor%20Is%20a%20Nature%20Lover%E2%80%99s%20Dream%20Destination%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20eve%20of%20her%2010th%20birthday%2C%20Mahima%20Sukhdev%E2%80%99s%20parents%20Vinati%20and%20Pavan%20posed%20a%20very%20important%20question%20to%20her%3A%20How%20would%20you%20like%20to%20celebrate%3F%20They%20had%20imagined%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20coloured%20responses%20%E2%80%94%20think%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20a%20little%20girl%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20fantasies%20%E2%80%94%20and%20weren%E2%80%99t%20prepared%20for%20the%20ask%20to%20be%20a%20trip%20to%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Borivali%20National%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325308%2Frare-wildlife-conservation-photos-from-across-the-world-nature-infocus-kalyan-varma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeep%20love%20for%20nature%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinati%20reminisces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20humoured%20by%20their%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20request%2C%20the%20couple%20went%20ahead%20and%20planned%20the%20nature%20trip.%20That%20day%2C%20Mahima%E2%80%99s%20friends%20returned%20home%20with%20beautiful%20return%20gifts%20%E2%80%94%20books%20that%20spoke%20of%20the%20birds%20and%20fauna%20at%20the%20national%20park.%20As%20Mahima%20grew%20older%2C%20her%20fascination%20for%20the%20outdoors%20only%20deepened.%20And%20whether%20it%20was%20nature%20trails%2C%20hikes%2C%20trips%20to%20safaris%20or%20afternoon%20picnics%2C%20her%20parents%20would%20always%20oblige.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelling%20these%20stories%20gets%20Vinati%20chuckling.%20After%20all%2C%20she%20sees%20them%20as%20jigsaw%20pieces%20that%20played%20a%20role%20in%20fortifying%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20nature.%20She%20says%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20Mahima%E2%80%99s%20passion%20rubbed%20off%20on%20her%2C%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20their%20daughter%20Ashima%2C%20and%20they%20grew%20as%20intrigued%20by%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinati%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20based%20in%20London%2C%20sees%20those%20years%20of%20innocence%20as%20the%20fabric%20that%20wove%20together%20the%20story%20of%20O%E2%80%99Land%20Plantation%20Stays%20%E2%80%94%20a%20120-acre%20estate%20which%20she%20manages.%20Set%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297379%2Fcouple-set-up-eco-friendly-homestay-in-nilgiris-jungle-hut-harvests-solar-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20of%20the%20Nilgiris%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20geographic%20salient%20that%20is%20spread%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%2C%20the%20stay%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20responsible%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20ever%20happen%20to%20be%20in%20Coonoor%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20recommend%3A%20Get%20into%20the%20car%2C%20stock%20it%20up%20with%20provisions%20that%20will%20last%20you%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20then%20drive.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20let%20the%20unsealed%20roads%20daunt%20you.%20Look%20for%20company%20in%20the%20spectacular%20scenery%20instead.%20Keep%20driving%20until%20you%20spot%20a%20carpet%20of%20green.%20This%20will%20be%20your%20first%20indication%20of%20having%20arrived%20at%20the%20O%E2%80%99Land%20Plantation%20Stay.%20The%20place%20is%20a%20great%20draw%20for%20bids%2C%20who%20a